comments: James (LAL) moves laterally into Brown's (BOS) path and turns his body when he makes contact with Brown's body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) reaches in and makes contact with Schroder's (LAL) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Schroder (LAL) delivers lower body contact to Walker (BOS), affecting his SQBR during his drive.
Brown (BOS) briefly engages and separates from Harrell (LAL) during the rebound.
Davis (LAL) places an incidental forearm on Tatum's (BOS) body as he moves along Tatum's path during the drive.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: James (LAL) loses control of the ball out of bounds.
Caruso (LAL) and Tatum (BOS) engage and disengage during the screen and the contact is marginal.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in Caruso's (LAL) path and makes marginal contact during the screen.
Harrell (LAL) makes marginal contact with Tatum's (BOS) body and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Walker (BOS) absorbs the contact with Davis (LAL) off-ball and does not affect his FOM.
Walker (BOS) makes clean contact to the ball as he dislodges it during Davis' (LAL) shot attempt in the post.
Caruso (LAL) and Brown (BOS) both make incidental contact as they move toward the pass in transition.
Walker (BOS) releases from Schroder (LAL) at the end of his drive.
Harrell (LAL) briefly engages and separates from Theis (BOS) during the rebound.
Harrell (LAL) makes marginal contact with Theis' (BOS) body during his shot attempt near the basket.
